{"tid":2275160,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Twice娜璉被網民連環指控整容導致唱高音失败","createTime":"2020-11-07T03:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T17:48:47.000Z","uid":320858,"like":12,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3e64b5ed86c1953ca25506e4e6331bb1da345a","tid":2275160,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/a9oxXSW9dzc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fa9oxXSW9dzc&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=c0e8f324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/a9oxXSW9dzc</a><br />\n<br />\n早就不行了吧 她鼻子都要成醫療事故了吧<br />\n蘋果肌也越看越可怕了，不知道是不是髮型的問題<br />\n<br />\n鼻孔的形狀都變了，應該是做過了吧&hellip;之前韓國人不是嫌棄她側面不好看來著嘛，心裡可能介意了<br />\n<br />\n能呼吸嗎👃，有眼睛的人應該都能看出來吧<br />\n<br />\n她剛出道臉就像充氣的呀，只不過越來越嚴重了而已<br />\n<br />\n越來越充氣娃娃<br />\n<br />\n這個貼頭皮髮型真的毀<br />\n<br />\n其實她以前鼻子就這樣吧&hellip;&hellip;這個造型不行<br />\n預告照山根就很奇怪<br />\n<br />\n確實，mv里更明顯<br />\n<br />\n她牙齒也很突大小不齊，為什麼大家喜歡她的嘴<br />\n<br />\n她的臉真的一看就u know what i mean 但之前人很靈動表情很可愛完全可以掩蓋掉違和感 最近可能該重新維修一下了<br />\n<br />\n動鼻子了，鼻梁跟額頭連接的地方很生硬，不知道為什麼要動，她鼻子也不醜，以前挺自然可愛<br />\n<br />\n天啊 娜鏈的鼻子好奇怪 臉崩得好可怕 她後面高音也唱崩了就算了 怎麼志效高音也有點要破音的感覺 她們這場是不是狀態不好啊<br />\n<br />\n吸氣鼻子都塞住了，沒氣就不能唱歌，難怪唱不上去<br />\n<br />\n評論認真的嗎？現在真是要求越來越低了，只要開口都有人誇<br />\n<br />\n鼻翼縮過頭了 ，要不就是蘋果肌打針過了點 ，顯得中庭太緊湊  尤其是這髮型完美暴露 不要搞貼頭皮了   前幾場帶貝雷帽轉移一下視覺焦點就挺好"},{"pid":"3c709c3fb2ef07556fe43f79ee770b645d34811a","tid":2275160,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6nP89X.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6nP89X.gif&h=c8293954&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1zLBO9Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1zLBO9Y.gif&h=961912e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OraNVPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOraNVPC.jpg&h=ceb85ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TavY2uN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTavY2uN.jpg&h=9add3070&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8116f3f0bba412a423bda2024bd5f7efaecec977","tid":2275160,"uid":7903,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f26f67fd143257bb70cfdb50705670ce689024","tid":2275160,"uid":374048,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:34:45.000Z","msg":"加翻有圖慎入會好啲 <br />\n一load到啲圖嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acefafb6df00a72d6bdcbbc415b72511912ded6b","tid":2275160,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8116f3f0bba412a423bda2024bd5f7efaecec977","tid":2275160,"uid":7903,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"Keyboard問題"},{"pid":"c67af4c91034c72a90c7507aa49cfea61ff454a7","tid":2275160,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:02:33.000Z","msg":"以前都幾可愛，點解而家變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fa622990148da4be74ae3f2f8e3847b02e4147","tid":2275160,"uid":37146,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:36:28.000Z","msg":"啲P牌閪真係煩"},{"pid":"32d1c729e88a1e7ec7519afaf9f2e4afade85231","tid":2275160,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:51:12.000Z","msg":"@適"},{"pid":"9ff84e5815ac328e7c7ffa5695c043f591387eed","tid":2275160,"uid":222155,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">化妝唔同咋死傻鳩，個個喺度黑我璉</span></span>"},{"pid":"f8d46ecdce9ce9ba079b8e8e2cbd35b4d1ea1b0a","tid":22751